definitions.definition: A failure , especially of a financial transaction ( a termination of an action ) .
A failing grade in an academic examination .
( slang , US ) A failure ( something incapable of success ) .
( uncountable , slang ) Poor quality ; substandard workmanship.
examples: The project was full of fail .
